# YAML-flavoured config parser

Canonical demo for `std/parsing/layout.ssc` (v1.20.2).  Parses a YAML-like
format where structure is conveyed entirely by indentation:

```
server:
  host: localhost
  port: 8080
  tls:
    cert: /etc/tls/cert.pem
    key:  /etc/tls/key.pem

database:
  host: db.internal
  port: 5432
  name: myapp
  pool:
    min: 2
    max: 10
```

No braces, no commas, no delimiters other than a colon and significant whitespace.

